data.description: Stunning Almaden Valley Oasis Minutes from It All. Welcome to 6352 Gondola Way - a tastefully updated 4 BD + Lower Level Bonus Rm as 5th BD RM/Office/Play RM/Den + 2.5BA charmer brimming w/ style & space in a premier Almaden neighborhood. This turnkey property boasts soaring vaulted ceilings, wide plank modern floors, custom tile work, & designer finishes throughout its light-filled open concept floor plan.The modern white kitchen is a chef's dream with Porcelanosa tile, sleek counters/cabinetry. Entertain in style w/ 2 separate family RM's, including 1 anchored by a cozy fireplace. Sliding doors blur indoor/outdoor living onto the large, flat backyard oasis w/ fresh landscaping - perfect for al fresco dining/entertaining this summer! 4 spacious BD's are located upstairs including the primary suite complete w/ double vanity bath, dual shower heads, & custom tiled shower niches. A bonus room on the lower level is ideal as a 5th BD, home office, Peloton RM, Zoom RM, or play RM. Just mins from DT Los Gatos' boutiques & eateries, top-rated schools: Castillero/Pioneer, local parks, & the Almaden Swim/Racket, this home's central location can't be beat. Close to major Tech Giants: Netflix: 5mi, Apple: 8mi, Cisco:10mi, Samsung:11mi, & PayPal:12mi. Welcome To Your Dream Home!
